data.description: Awesome home with a ton of privacy for sale! You are going to fall in love with this charming home on a quiet street. Very well kept 3/2/2 with large back yard offering a ton of privacy. The huge kitchen has new SS appliances, plenty of counterspace, and an abundance of storage. Split bedroom plan with spacious master suite. Sellers absolutely love their home, just want to move closer to family. Come make it your own, but hurry it wont last long!
